Key Takeaways:

Always use specific principals in trust policies, never wildcards
Implement Condition statements (ExternalId, MFA) for additional security
Regularly audit role trust policies for misconfigurations
Monitor CloudTrail logs for suspicious AssumeRole activity
Apply principle of least privilege to all IAM roles
